(25, 'The Oxford and Cambridge University Boat Race', 'Short, News, Sport', 'Although the content of this film is primitive in the extreme - a shot of the traditional Oxford versus Cambridge University Boat Race, filmed on March 30 1895 - this film is of immense historical importance as being the first ever British film—Michael Brooke <michael@everyman.demon.co.uk>', 'NA', 'None', 'United Kingdom', '', 9, 25, 4, 'Birt Acres, Robert W. Paul', 45, '', '', '', 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BOGFiZjVkYmYtYjkwZC00NWY0LWI0MGItYWYyNzNlMDNlN2Y2XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNzg5OTk2OA@@.jpg'),
