(27, 'Cordeliers\' Square in Lyon', 'Documentary, Short', 'A stationary camera looks across the boulevard at a diagonal toward one corner of Lyon\'s Cordeliers\' Square. It\'s a long shot, with a great deal of depth of focus. We can see the sky and fronts of four buildings, each four or five stories tall. It\'s a busy thoroughfare, with pedestrians walking in front of the buildings and crossing the boulevard between horse-drawn vehicles. A double-decker bus passes in front of us, pulled by two horses. Various tradesmen pass on wagons. One van passes.—<jhailey@hotmail.com>', '1', 'None', 'France', '', 1, 23, 6, 'Lumière', 1214, '', '', '', 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BYzc4ZTA4NmItMDdkZS00NWZjLWFjYjQtZjMzYjk5YjVhMTdkXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyODgzNDIwODA@.jpg'),
(28, 'Fishing for Goldfish', 'Documentary, Short', 'A baby held by his father dips his little hands into a water jug and he can\' t catch the goldfish .', '1', 'None', 'France', '', 10, 24, 5, 'Lumière', 1142, 'Andrée Lumière, Auguste Lumière', '', '', 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BYTNkN2I5MGUtMWVmOS00OWE5LWE4ZDMtZjE1NjJiODJkNDc5L2ltYWdlL2ltYWdlXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNzg5OTk2OA@@.jpg'),
(29, 'Baby\'s Meal', 'Documentary, Short', 'As part of a maiden public film screening at the Salon Indien, on December 28, in Paris, Auguste Lumière pivots the centre of attention around his baby daughter, as he tries to feed her from a spoon.', '1', 'None', 'France', '', 10, 1, 6, 'Lumière', 3529, 'Mrs. Auguste Lumiere, Andrée Lumière, Auguste Lumière', '', '', 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BM2Q0ZDhkM2EtODFlOC00NzRiLWJhMmYtMmI0ZWQ0ZTdmMzBmXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNDE5MTU2MDE@.jpg'),
(30, 'Rough Sea at Dover', 'Documentary, Short', 'The sea is quite rough, and at Dover a series of heavy waves pounds against a pier and along the adjacent shoreline. The scene then shifts to a different view of flowing water, and shows a heavy current from a point along a riverbank.', '1', 'None', 'United Kingdom', '', 10, 4, 5, 'Birt Acres, Robert W. Paul', 898, '', '', '', 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BOWFhNTM4MmYtMTBjZi00MWMyLWEyMjYtNjAwODcyM2U2NzM1XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNTM3MDMyMDQ@.jpg'),
(31, 'Jumping the Blanket', 'Documentary, Short', 'Outdoors, with a nondescript building in the background, four men stand, each holding the corner of a blanket stretched parallel to the ground. They wear the clothes of laborers. By the back corner on our left stands a uniformed man who seems in charge. A sixth man stands back from the blanket about six paces; he runs forward and takes a leap but stops at the edge of the blanket and is upbraided by the uniformed gent. The same thing happens a second time, but the next three times, he completes a flip, landing on his back in the middle of the blanket, and the four then boost him out toward the camera. The final time seems like it will be his last for awhile.—<jhailey@hotmail.com>', '1', 'None', 'France', '', 5, 8, 6, 'Lumière', 1052, '', '', '', 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNmY3YTM2MTQtNWY5MC00MzQxLWJiMDctNWYzYTI5N2Y1OGEzXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyODgzNDIwODA@.jpg'),
(32, 'Die Serpentintänzerin', 'Short', 'The seventh sequence of the \"Wintergartenprogramm (1895)\" by the Skladanowsky Brothers. In it, a young female dancer with large, flowing robes, swirls round herself quickly, making her light robe flow around her like a butterfly\'s wings.', '1', 'None', 'Germany', '', 7, 4, 5, '', 437, 'Ancion', '', '', 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BYzEzMGUyNjQtNTRjZC00OGY1LThmMTYtM2UwM2Q0ZWM3NzE2XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNzg5OTk2OA@@.jpg'),
