(36, 'Awakening of Rip', 'Drama, Short', 'The seventh of eight short black and white films from director William K.L. Dickson in which he chronicles the story of Rip Van Winkle. In this film, Rip awakes from his slumber, having significantly aged during his sleep.', '1', 'None', 'United States', '', 1, 16, 4, 'American Mutoscope Company', 622, 'Joseph Jefferson', '', '', 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BZWM1OGIxYzYtMzI1ZC00NDZmLWEzNmMtOTc2Y2JjNTQ0NDAyL2ltYWdlL2ltYWdlXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNzg5OTk2OA@@.jpg'),
